name: Spread The Memes Darkside x Magic53

metadata.name: UncleSeize Darkside
metadata.description:
UncleShred Darkside is derived from "UncleSeize", a genesis NFT from Punk6529's "The Memes by 6529" collection. 

The Memes Collection by 6529 is focused on the fight for the open metaverse (decentralisation, community, self-sovereignty) and spreading this message to many people, many wallets. 

The Darkside series questions benevolence while wielding great power. Do foundational principals and objectives outweigh the wishes of a self-sovereign community?
